etica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\tSubtle<br />\n\tSubtle means something that is not obvious, perhaps slightly hidden. What is subtle? Why is it subtle? What is the outcome?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They saw a subtle movement... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) subtle body language<br />\n\t2) subtle message<br />\n\t3) subtle change in atmosphere<br />\n\t4) subtle design<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tSure enough, the meeting wrapped up soon after a short discussion, and the interior having shown a few quick sketches to the club manager. The manager seemed to like the idea of adding more subtle storage space. The interior designed suggested changing up some of the artwork, but the owner of the office seemed to be set on keeping the two art pieces: the hanging painting on the back wall as well as the delicate sculpture sitting near the coffee table. The interior had seen that art piece before and knew that it was listed in an exhibition a short while ago.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/166982146782/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p768171/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p768171\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul st